Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛斯王国？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是这个大陆的中心 很热闹对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和阿利亚差多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…克劳德 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 现在不是做这种事情的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此唐突地前来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能得到您的接见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是由衷的感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷吉斯还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是那么顽固吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你叫克劳德是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是、是的 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想调查索沙陨石是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索沙陨石所在的艾尔大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受其影响所产生的魔物们\N目前还处于和人们交战的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还没有战况传来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过胜利的话应该就会有所传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我国派出的特使至今也还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可能会是一趟赌上性命的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此你也还是要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再问你们一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可不要后悔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通行证你们拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是到艾尔大陆的通行证啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往来大陆之间居然需要通行证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想可能就拿不到这张通行证呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是你的功劳哟 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点事没什么好谢的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.87,0:03:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真的好紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然国王的那种威严好庄严啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我识相点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看该识相点的人应该是你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太缠人的男人可不受欢迎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要以为你是女人我们才来陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是听说你要找保镖才来找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 我不是拒绝了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事哪是你说了就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总要把理由说清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得太丑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们三个并不是我喜欢的类型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 你们还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自以为是女人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.58,0:04:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三大男人欺负一个女人太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小兄弟 想打架吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有没有听见啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定选你当我的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个…我们的话可还没说完呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用你的脏手碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敢碰我的身体 就得有相当的觉悟的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.22,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要做个了断了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 很危险哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家退后一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会再手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我们怎么修理你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡于吾体内的红莲之火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉火界王派蒙之名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此解放汝等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在圣三角的引导下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将阻挡在吾面前者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给予灼热的制裁！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焰之矢！(Fire Bolt)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫塞丽奴•茱莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我叫做克劳德……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德 那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,え什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经是我的保镖了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那、那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛斯洞窟马上就要到了哟 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德在搞什么嘛 还会不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来和我们的目的地完全不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛斯的秘宝到底是什么样的宝藏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里好兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝藏猎人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是一流的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的招术呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你不知道 纹章术 吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纹章术？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用刻画在身上某种特定形状的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将念力转换成各种不同形态的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分为空气 水 火 地 等图形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将天魔之名作为烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能作为 纹章术 使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿我来说 像我刚才使用火系法术的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是利用掌管 火 的三角形的纹章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三角形的纹章…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 浮现在这里哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…我好象没有要你一起跟过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么需要克劳德呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过让他做我的保镖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够使用那种纹章术的纹章术师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好象不需要什么保镖的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的目的又不是宝藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是索沙陨石才对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索沙陨石…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这是我听来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说克洛斯洞窟由于索沙陨石的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好象受到影响什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到索沙陨石的影响？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗 塞丽奴小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的 我没听过这样的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也只能怪你的消息不够灵通咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到镇上问问看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在就去确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实根本就没这回事哟^^
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是真的到了那里就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经有白跑一趟的心理准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总比没去 事后后悔要来的好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然克劳德你都这么说了……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就往克洛斯洞窟前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象中的还要大哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都是湿湿的…感觉很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 这么快就有岔路了啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走哪一边呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看地图吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么黑看不到哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要我去弄点火照亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.86,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在混浊之泉沐浴的明界王拉格苏醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是纹章术师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 ……这张是藏宝图吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:09:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太没礼貌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我在克洛斯王国最大的拍卖会上\N好不容易竞标得来的真品哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还附有鉴定书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏宝图居然会有坚定书 这不是很可疑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 走左边这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受不了现在的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点跟上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太没用了吧 只不过是蝙蝠而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这是人家第一次看到蝙蝠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地方真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西受到了索沙陨石的影响吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯…真的有…真的有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果还不能走路就再休息一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的没有事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好  年轻就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过麻烦你们走快一点好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀？这还真是怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又没路了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是第七次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一直照着地图走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地图上画的还有路可走的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地图果然是假货嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回头吧 快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你惹她生气了哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀……讨厌虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:24.32,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌虫子啦 讨厌讨厌……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等 塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是她要雇佣保镖的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把虫子丢掉了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她这个人还真可爱…呃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…人家吓得心跳得好快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞利奴…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西…过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫…虫…虫子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大一条！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这是什么跟什么啊 真是受不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人还真诚实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过肚子还真是饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些饼干如果可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客气咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有一点受潮 但是这个时候就凑合着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴小姐 这些饼干是为了克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了　我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的你们两个就分着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下一块了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请拿去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我肚子还不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一人一半
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？　克劳德…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀　还挺亲热的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞…塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是叫人羡慕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当个一流的宝藏猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有谈恋爱得空闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是在炫耀？还是在埋怨？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张地图一定是假的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可知道我花了多少钱才买到它的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:14:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家的胸部会被磨小的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算是什么啊　真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦　这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是歪打正着　运气真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神殿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是旧文明的遗址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们好象被塞丽奴小姐给唬弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里根本没有什么跟索沙陨石有关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的　果然塞丽奴她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？话说回来塞丽奴小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边这边　你们俩快点过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛斯的秘宝？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝藏发现了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里装了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀？你不是没感兴趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么石像…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是索沙陨石的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些石像上附着守护灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前曾经听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旧文明时代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫廷的纹章术师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了守护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便让灵魂附着在武器或者是石像上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 居然弹开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它根本就毫发无伤嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么样才能打倒它们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是一会儿也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能帮我暂时缠住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想试试一个纹章术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这个咒文的咒语很长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在咒语咏唱的途中被他们打断的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咒文就无法完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物们　宝藏在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在赤圣三角的引导下 控制火的火界王派蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在银新月的引导下 控制水的水界王亚里顿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在金正方的引导下 控制地的地界王阿迈蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在青圆的引导下　控制月的空气界王奥里姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在支配自然界的汝等之佑护下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引导这蓝锥圆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昭示天地四方 古往今来的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥抱吾等的四方境界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完吗　塞丽奴？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.28,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,掌管万物的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:00.92,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,以照耀四方的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞利奴　快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:05.32,Top,NTP,0,0,0,,赐予吾等白术之光吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞丽奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这招用起来果然辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面写了什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是更大的藏宝地点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个宝藏还真是出人意料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托 你说你要跟我们一起走 是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保镖的工作已经结束了吧 塞利奴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道镇上有一家不错餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.92,0:20:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜景也很漂亮 非常浪漫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说"啊…是吗…"的时候吧 克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫子～
